Draconic Lineage		KEY:Trait ~ Draconic Lineage						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.RaceTrait				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.RaceTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Draconic Lineage]											DESC:You gain a +1 trait bonus on saving throws against fear and against any effect created by a creature of the dragon type. If you gain a bloodrager or sorcerer bloodline, you must choose draconic.																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.3	ASPECT:SaveBonus|+1 on saves vs. fear and vs. any effects created by creatures of the dragon type.
