Dragon Pact			KEY:Trait ~ Dragon Pact							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SocialTrait				PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.SocialTrait],[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Dragon Pact]											DESC:Choose one category of true dragon (chromatic, metallic, primal, etc.). You gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks against that category of dragon and a +1 trait bonus on Intimidate checks against all creatures of the dragon type that are not of the same category of true dragon.																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.3
